### 9. ARCHITECTURE SUMMARY - DATA FLOW

**Current (embedded) flow**:
```
User message
  ↓
Chat agent invokes PM agent tool
  ↓
PM agent returns PmAgentOutput with SubagentTrace
  ↓
chat-route.ts onFinish extracts trace from tool part
  ↓
Trace persisted as subagent_traces array on message record
  ↓
workspace-routes/branch-chain query message.subagent_traces
  ↓
API returns subagentTraces in WorkspaceBootstrapMessage
```

**Target (normalized) flow**:
```
User message
  ↓
Chat agent invokes PM agent tool
  ↓
PM agent returns PmAgentOutput with SubagentTrace
  ↓
chat-route.ts onFinish creates trace records:
  - Root trace with type: "subagent_spawn"
  - Child traces with parent_trace references
  ↓
chat-route.ts creates spawns edge: RELATE message:msg1 ->spawns-> trace:root1
  ↓
workspace-routes/branch-chain query SELECT ->spawns->trace FROM message
  ↓
Reconstruct SubagentTrace from trace record hierarchy
  ↓
API returns subagentTraces in WorkspaceBootstrapMessage (same wire format)
```

