  - *Mitigation*: Batch load all spawns edges + child traces in 2 queries
- `FLEXIBLE` object field type mismatches (low probability, medium impact)
  - *Mitigation*: Explicit field mapping in reconstruction logic
- Frontend wire format mismatch (low probability, high impact)
  - *Mitigation*: API contract type unchanged; acceptance test validates shape

